  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to find a radiological biomarker of Transient Ischemic Attacks (TIA)
      thanks to functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging (fMRI) done within the 24 hour after symptoms
      onset.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
